d and stylish. With its advanced features, including fitness tracking and notifications, it's the perfect companion for your active lifestyle.\",\n      image: imageSrc\n    }, {\n      id: 5,\n      name: \"Apple Watch\",\n      category: \"Phones\",\n      price: \"$35\",\n      quantity: 20,\n      creation_date: \"2024-05-01\",\n      description: \"a sleek and smart wearable that keeps you connected and stylish. With its advanced features, including fitness tracking and notifications, it's the perfect companion for your active lifestyle.\",\n      image: imageSrc\n    }, {\n      id: 6,\n      name: \"Apple Watch\",\n      category: \"Phones\",\n      price: \"$35\",\n      quantity: 20,\n      creation_date: \"2024-05-01\",\n      description: \"a sleek and smart wearable that keeps you connected and stylish. With its advanced features, including fitness tracking and notifications, it's the perfect companion for your active lifestyle.\",\n      image: imageSrc\n    }, {\n      id: 7,\n      name: \"Apple Watch\",\n      category: \"Phones\",\n      price: \"$35\",\n      quantity: 20,\n      creation_date: \"2024-05-01\",\n      description: \"a sleek and smart wearable that keeps you connected and stylish. With its advanced features, including fitness tracking and notifications, it's the perfect companion for your active lifestyle.\",\n      image: imageSrc\n    }];\n    return {\n      selectedProduct: null,\n      // Store selected product data\n      showModal: false,\n      showInfoModal: false,\n      showEditModal: false,\n      products,\n      showDeleteModalFlag: false,\n      productToDelete: null,\n      dropDownCategory: false,\n      showNewCategoryInput: false,\n      newCategoryName: \"\",\n      selectedCategory: null,\n      categories: [{\n        id: 1,\n        name: \"TV/Monitors\"\n      }, {\n        id: 2,\n        name: \"TV/Monitors\"\n      }, {\n        id: 3,\n        name: \"TV/Monitors\"\n      }, {\n        id: 4,\n        name: \"TV/Monitors\"\n      }, \"Gaming/Console\", \"Phones\"]\n    };\n  },\n  methods: {\n    // Method to handle info button click and set selectedProduct\n    showProductInfo(product) {\n      this.selectedProduct = product;\n      this.showInfoModal = true;\n    },\n    // Method to handle edit button click and set selectedProduct\n    showProductEdit(product) {\n      this.selectedProduct = product;\n      this.showEditModal = true;\n    },\n    handleSaveChanges(editedProduct) {\n      // Find the index of the edited product in the products array\n      const index = this.products.findIndex(product => product.id === editedProduct.id);\n      if (index !== -1) {\n        // Update the product data in the products array\n        this.products[index] = editedProduct;\n      }\n      // Close the edit modal\n      this.showEditModal = false;\n    },\n    showDeleteModal(product) {\n      this.showDeleteModalFlag = true;\n      this.productToDelete = product;\n    },\n    closeDeleteModal() {\n      this.showDeleteModalFlag = false;\n      this.productToDelete = null;\n    },\n    deleteProduct() {\n      if (this.productToDelete) {\n        // Assuming you have an array of products, remove the product\n        const index = this.products.findIndex(product => product.id === this.productToDelete.id);\n        if (index !== -1) {\n          this.products.splice(index, 1);\n        }\n        // You may need to make an API call to delete the product from the server as well\n      }\n      this.closeDeleteModal();\n    },\n    // Method to add new product to the products array\n    addNewProduct(newProduct) {\n      // Generate a unique id for the new product (you may need to modify this logic)\n      const id = this.products.length + 1;\n      // Add the id to the new product object\n      newProduct.id = id;\n      // Push the new product to the products array\n      this.products.push(newProduct);\n    },\n    selectCategory(category) {\n      this.selectedCategory = category;\n    },\n    toggleNewCategoryInput() {\n      this.showNewCategoryInput = !this.showNewCategoryInput; // Toggle the visibility of the input field and add button\n      if (!this.showNewCategoryInput) {\n        this.newCategoryName = \"\"; // Clear the input field if it's hidden\n      }\n    },\n    addNewCategory() {\n      if (this.newCategoryName.trim() !== \"\") {\n        // Check if the new category name is not empty\n        this.categories.push(this.newCategoryName); // Add the new category to the categories array\n        this.newCategoryName = \"\"; // Clear the input field after adding the category\n        this.toggleNewCategoryInput(); // Hide the input field and add button after adding the category\n      }\n    },\n    deleteCategory(index) {\n      this.categories.splice(index, 1);\n    }\n  },\n  computed: {\n    // Computed property to filter products based on selected category\n    filteredProducts() {\n      if (!this.selectedCategory) {\n        return this.products; // Return all products if no category is selected\n      } else {\n        // Filter products based on selected category\n        return this.products.filter(product => product.category === this.selectedCategory);\n      }\n    }\n  }\n};","map":{"version":3,"names":["imageSrc","ProductModal","InfoProdModal","DeleteProdModal","EditProdModal","name","components","data","products","id","category","price","quantity","creation_date","description","image","selectedProduct","showModal","showInfoModal","showEditModal","showDeleteModalFlag","productToDelete","dropDownCategory","showNewCategoryInput","newCategoryName","selectedCategory","categories","methods","showProductInfo","product","showProductEdit","handleSaveChanges","editedProduct","index","findIndex","showDeleteModal","closeDeleteModal","deleteProduct","splice","addNewProduct","newProduct","length","push","selectCategory","toggleNewCategoryInput","addNewCategory","trim","deleteCategory","computed","filteredProducts","filter"],"sources":["C:\\Users\\hp\\ShoppableApplication\\admin\\src\\views\\Products.vue"],"sourcesContent":["<template>\r\n  <main id=\"Product-page\">\r\n    <form class=\"flex items-center ml-12 mt-20 relative\">\r\n      <label for=\"search\" class=\"sr-only\">Search</label>\r\n      <div class=\"flex items-center relative w-full\">\r\n        <div\r\n          class=\"absolute inset-y-0 start-0 flex items-center ps-3 pointer-events-none\"\r\n        >\r\n          <svg\r\n            class=\"w-4 h-4 me-2\"\r\n            xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"\r\n            fill=\"none\"\r\n            viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"\r\n          >\r\n            <path\r\n              stroke=\"#8a8a8a\"\r\n              stroke-linecap=\"round\"\r\n              stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\r\n              stroke-width=\"2\"\r\n              d=\"m19 19-4-4m0-7A7 7 0 1 1 1 8a7 7 0 0 1 14 0Z\"\r\n            />\r\n          </svg>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <input\r\n          type=\"text\"\r\n          id=\"search\"\r\n          class=\"bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-sm rounded-lg focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 block ps-10 p-2.5\"\r\n          placeholder=\"Search ...\"\r\n          style=\"width: 20rem\"\r\n        />\r\n        <div class=\"relative\">\r\n          <button\r\n            id=\"dropdowncatButton\"\r\n            class=\"text-white bg-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-600 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-gray-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 mx-5 py-2.5 text-center inline-flex items-center\"\r\n            type=\"button\"\r\n            @click=\"dropDownCategory = !dropDownCategory\"\r\n          >\r\n            Category\r\n            <svg\r\n              class=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 ms-3\"\r\n              xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"\r\n              fill=\"none\"\r\n              viewBox=\"0 0 10 6\"\r\n            >\r\n              <path\r\n                stroke=\"currentColor\"\r\n                stroke-linecap=\"round\"\r\n                stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\r\n                stroke-width=\"2\"\r\n                d=\"m1 1 4 4 4-4\"\r\n              />\r\n            </svg>\r\n          </button>\r\n\r\n          <!-- Dropdown menu -->\r\n          <div\r\n            v-if=\"dropDownCategory\"\r\n            class=\"absolute z-30 top-12 left-0 bg-white rounded-lg shadow w-60\"\r\n          >\r\n            <ul class=\"h-48 py-2 overflow-y-auto text-left text-gray-700\">\r\n              <li v-for=\"(category, index) in categories\" :key=\"index\">\r\n                <div class=\"block flex justify-between\">\r\n                  <div class=\"px-4 py-2\">\r\n                    <a\r\n                      href=\"#\"\r\n                      class=\"hover:bg-gray-100\"\r\n                      @click=\"selectCategory(category)\"\r\n                    >\r\n                      {{ category }}\r\n                    </a>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <div class=\"flex h-8 px-4 py-2\">\r\n                    <svg\r\n                      xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"\r\n                      viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"\r\n                      class=\"cursor-pointer\"\r\n                      @click=\"deleteCategory(index)\"\r\n                    >\r\n                      <path\r\n                        fill=\"#b92525\"\r\n                        d=\"M135.2 17.7C140.6 6.8 151.7 0 163.8 0H284.2c12.1 0 23.2 6.8 28.6 17.7L320 32h96c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32s-14.3 32-32 32H32C14.3 96 0 81.7 0 64S14.3 32 32 32h96l7.2-14.3zM32 128H416V448c0 35.3-28.7 64-64 64H96c-35.3 0-64-28.7-64-64V128zm96 64c-8.8 0-16 7.2-16 16V432c0 8.8 7.2 16 16 16s16-7.2 16-16V208c0-8.8-7.2-16-16-16zm96 0c-8.8 0-16 7.2-16 16V432c0 8.8 7.2 16 16 16s16-7.2 16-16V208c0-8.8-7.2-16-16-16zm96 0c-8.8 0-16 7.2-16 16V432c0 8.8 7.2 16 16 16s16-7.2 16-16V208c0-8.8-7.2-16-16-16z\"\r\n                      />\r\n                    </svg>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n  